{
  "stem": "1169.2",
  "chunk_idx": 11,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 12.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And it says, dear rabbi, we are being treated well.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "We are working.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And best regards, signed such and such.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "[NON-ENGLISH] This Valdeza-- of course we did not realize-- was a fictitious entity somewhere in hell, I would say.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "It just did not exist.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "It was a deception.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And everyone who was about to be killed was asked to write this postcard.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And they stamp marked it Valdeza.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "We thought there is a Valdeza.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "But there was no Valdeza.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And we really figured that everyone is being taken to Valdeza.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And the rumor was that because the gentiles had this propaganda there that the Jews are lazy, they are only into their professions, they should do some physical work.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "This is really how we bought the story.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "They want us to do physical work.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "They don't like that we should be doctors or lawyers.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "We should do physical work.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And here in Valdeza, it's like a re-education village.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And they will teach us to do productive, physical labor.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And we were certain that everyone's going to Valdeza.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "And we knew that one of these days, the war is going to come to an end.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "And so we will survive Valdeza.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "It's a question of a year or a few months.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "We will survive it.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "And everybody thought that we were going to Valdeza.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] In fact, this customer once visited my grandpa in Vienna.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "And my grandfather told him, you know, I assume that my family is in Valdeza.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "So the customer said, you know, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] he said, [NON-ENGLISH SPEECH].",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "He used that expression to my grandfather.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "That's a deception.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "There's no Valdeza.",
      "word_count": 3
    }
  ],
